Package: PopulationStructure
Type: Package
Title: Performs PCA Analysis Using PLINK, Identifies Outlier Individuals, and Produces Publication-Ready Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Devashish Tripathi
Maintainer: Devashish Tripathi <devashishtripathi697@gmail.com>
Description: Implements a comprehensive PCA pipeline utilizing PLINK, widely used in genomic data analysis. The pipeline's design incorporates parameter settings from the Genome Asia 100K project, ensuring robustness and contemporary relevance. Users are responsible for installing PLINK. For details on PLINK installation, refer to its official documentation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
